        dc:description           "Figure 6. Imbachoculodes namhaensis gen. et sp. nov., holotype, male, 3.6 mm: (A) habitus; (B) head; (C) antenna 1; (D) antenna 2; (E) lower lip (only half shown); (F) right mandible; (G) left mandible; (H) maxilla 1; (I) maxilla 2; (J) maxilliped. Scale bars = 0.4 mm (A), 0.2 mm (B–D), 0.05 mm (E–J)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4652613/files/figure.png" .

