        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 8. Imbachoculodes namhaensis gen. et sp. nov., holotype, male, 3.6 mm: (A) pereopod 7; (B) uropod 1; (C) uropod 2; (D) uropod 3; (E) telson; Imbachoculodes namhaensis gen. et sp. nov., paratype, female, 4.1 mm: (F) habitus; (G) head; (H) antenna 1; (I) antenna 2; (J) right mandible. Scale bars = 0.4 mm (F), 0.2 mm (A, G), 0.1 mm (B–E, H–J)." ;
